Вакансія від 11 березня 2020
Business Analyst CVM (SQL)
Київстар
· VIP
Телекомунікації, зв'язок;
більше 1000 співробітників
Київ, вулиця Дегтярівська, 53.
6,9 км від центру ·
На мапі
Повна зайнятість, готові взяти студента.
Досвід роботи від 2 років.
Вища освіта.
Опис вакансії
Main responsibilities
Participate in development and verification of CVM revenue methodology
Conducting regular effectiveness evaluation studies on CVM campaigns
Preparation of regular & ad-hoc analytical reports
Subscribers base segmentation
Implementation & support of online analytical dashboards
Building an effective dialogue and cross-functional cooperation (within Commercial department and with Operational Companies) in business decisions making process
We are looking for someone who has:
Degree in Finance, Economics, Marketing or Management received in reputable university
2−3 years of relevant experience, preferably, in telecom analytics, CRM, marketing
Intermediate English; Russian and Ukrainian both spoken and written
Knowledge of SQL
Strong analytical and data visualization skills
Advanced user of excel (modeling), data mining skills
Ability to learn quickly, multi-task and excellent time-management
Strong project management, interpersonal and organizational skills
Working at VEON demands a high standard of business ethics and adherence to our legal obligations, our values and our Code of Conduct and supporting compliance policies and procedures. Our pioneering spirit is embodied in our values to be customer obsessed, entrepreneurial, innovative, collaborative, and truthful. Being truthful requires us to act ethically, honestly, and with integrity.
